  ('generalpolice-8b7f1efc-moex-00391', 'generalpolice-8b7f1efc', 'generalpolice-8b7f1efc-moex-110-de0a21a2', 'sub-generalpolice-8b7f1efc-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲女某日獨自於戶外郊遊，行經一個陌生僻靜之處，突然見到 A男在該
